{"tid":1096702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳移民政策不咬弦 美國國土安全部長換人","createTime":"2019-04-08T01:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T09:03:30.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b3b669a66645f910f1eb0f0a792a458b10546959","tid":1096702,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:34:52.000Z","msg":"【新增影片】 美國總統特朗普在Twitter宣佈國土安全部長尼爾森(Kirstjen Nielsen)離職，並由海關與邊境保衞局長麥克萊南(Kevin McAleenan)署任國土安全部長。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普又在Twitter中，感謝尼爾森的服務。有知情人士透露，尼爾森早前與特朗普巡視完邊境後，周日到了白宮再與特朗普會面，據報尼爾森對於長期以來，未能調動其他政府部門配合應付非法移民家庭入境，感到沮喪。<br />\n<br />\n今年46歲的尼爾森在2017年12月就任國土安全部長，但自去年中期選舉後，已經有傳尼爾森因移民政策與特朗普不咬弦，將自行離職。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190408/large/1554676486_88ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190408%2Flarge%2F1554676486_88ac.jpg&h=b8854046&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特朗普在Twitter宣佈尼爾森離任國土安全部長(路透社<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190408/59461796\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190408%2F59461796&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUVm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=1d41a8ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190408%2F59461796&h=b42b234e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190408/59461796</a>"},{"pid":"337e02251eeb76624eec04af2e6071502dd6a45d","tid":1096702,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:43:37.000Z","msg":"女人做呢個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47c05a91050701b03d0915780b1b670e8b2fb7e","tid":1096702,"uid":9286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"337e02251eeb76624eec04af2e6071502dd6a45d","tid":1096702,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"scor